&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovL3d3dy5jdGZzLXdpa2kuY29tL0ZJL0ZJLnBocD9maWxlbmFtZT10ZXN0LnR4dA==&#34;&gt;http://www.ctfs-wiki.com/FI/FI.php?filename=test.txt&lt;/span&gt;.................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................................&lt;/p&gt;
